# =============================================================================
# WHAT YOU SHOULD COMMIT (for reference)
# =============================================================================
# These are NOT ignored - documenting for clarity:
#
# Source code:
#   - All .py, .rs, .go, .js, .ts, .c, .cpp, .java, .rb, .lua, .pl, .sh, .php files
#   - Configuration files (without secrets)
#   - Makefiles, build scripts
#   - Tests
#
# Dependency manifests:
#   - package.json, Cargo.toml, go.mod, requirements.txt, Gemfile, composer.json
#   - Lock files (if uncommented above)
#
# Documentation:
#   - README.md, docs/, *.md
#   - LICENSE
#   - CHANGELOG.md
#
# Configuration (without secrets):
#   - .gitignore, .gitattributes
#   - .editorconfig
#   - CI/CD configs (.github/, .gitlab-ci.yml)
#   - Docker files (Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml)
#
# Static assets (reasonable size):
#   - Images, fonts, icons (for web projects)
#   - CSS, SCSS
#   - HTML templates
#
# =============================================================================

# End of template - customize above for your specific project
